          <h1 class="text-center mb-4">About Writle</h1>
          <p>Welcome to Writle, your innovative platform designed to streamline your writing process and enhance your creative endeavors. Writle is crafted with the understanding that every narrative is a complex tapestry of ideas, characters, and themes. Our goal is to provide you with a comprehensive tool that not only stores your projects but also organizes them in a way that enriches your writing experience.</h1>
